      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MUMMA EASY (6) chases a hat-trick of wins after flying the lids with a sensational early split last time, going on to clock 19.19 when a 1.75 lengths winner over 350m at this track. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Hard to fault her recent form and can win again. BORROLOOLA BOY (7) finished in the minors last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 300m at this track, taking a T3 RSTW in a powerful 16.60. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. RED RIVER ROGUE (1) was well in the market last time but only managed fourth (17.36), beaten 9 lengths. Finished second the start before. The form out of last race has been strong. Should be in this for a long way. ASTON ALERT (2) deserves plenty of thought over this distance.",
